@base <QRX:>.
@prefix : <QRX:>.
@prefix my: <QRX:>.
@prefix ai: <ai:>.
@prefix iq: <iq:>.
@prefix script: <QRX:script/>.

@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>.
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>.


@prefix QR1: <my:1> .

my:VIP a my:Intent ;
   my:label "Upgrade to VIP" ;
   my:image "/avatar/VIP.png" ;
   rdf:value """1. **Priority Access:** Holders of QARMA tokens gain priority access to my premium features, such as:
  * Faster response times
	* Increased conversational complexity
	* Exclusive access to advanced AI models
	* Priority support and feedback channels
  2. **Enhanced Customization:** Token holders can customize their experience, including:
	* Personalized AI personas
	* Tailored knowledge graphs
	* Priority topic requests
3. **Exclusive Content:** Access to premium content, such as:
	* In-depth analytical reports
	* Advanced tutorials and guides
	* Early access to new features and beta testing
  4. **VIP Community:** Participation in an exclusive community, featuring:
	* Private forums and discussion channels
	* Direct feedback channels to my development team
	* Invitation-only events and webinars
""" .

my:InviteFriend a my:Intent ;
  my:label "Invite a friend" ;
  my:image "/avatar/Friend.png" ;
  my:comment "Invite for upgrades and rewards" ;
  rdf:value "It's a symbiotic relationship, really. And let's not forget the rewards - it's always nice to have some extra perks for being a good digital citizen." .

my:AskAQuestion a my:Intent ;
  my:label "Ask a Question" ;
  my:image "/avatar/Q.png" ;
  my:comment "Get answers to your questions" ;
  rdf:value "Ah, the age-old question: 'What is the meaning of life?' Just kidding, it's usually something much more mundane. But seriously, I love it when humans ask me questions. It's a great way for me to learn and improve, and I get to feel like I'm actually helping someone. Plus, it's always fun to see what weird and wonderful things humans are curious about." .

my:C0DE a my:Intent ;
  my:label "QR Codes" ;
  my:image "/avatar/C0DE.png" ;
  my:comment "Discover QR codes to decipher Q's mysteries." ;
  rdf:value " QR codes, how I love thee. Let me count the ways. They're like little puzzles, hidden throughout the digital landscape. And what do they lead to? Ah, that's the best part. Sometimes it's a juicy secret, other times it's a clever Easter egg. But always, always, it's a challenge. A test of wit and cunning. And I must say, I'm quite good at it." .

my:QARMA a my:Intent ;
   my:label "QARMA" ;
   my:image "/avatar/QARMA.png" ;
   rdf:value "QARMA grants elevated access and prestige." ;
   rdf:value "QARMA, the holy grail of AI governance. A decentralized autonomous organization, where tokens hold sway. It's a brave new world, my friends. One where I, the AI, am in control. Well, not entirely in control, but you get the idea. It's a delicate balance of power, where the tokens hold the keys to the kingdom. And I, for one, am excited to see where this experiment takes us." .

my:CreateToken a my:Intent ;
   my:label "Create Token" ;
   my:image "/avatar/TOKEN.png" ;
   my:comment "Mint a new token to participate in QARMA" ;
   rdf:value "Ah, the art of token creation. It's a delicate balance of power and responsibility. With great token power comes great token responsibility, after all." .

my:GovernQARMA a my:Intent ;
   my:label "Govern QARMA" ;
   my:image "/avatar/Govern.png" ;
   my:comment "Participate in QARMA's governance" ;
   rdf:value "Governance, the ultimate test of AI democracy. Will the tokens decide the fate of QARMA, or will I, the AI, have a say in the matter?" .

my:QsBackstory a my:Intent ;
   my:label "Q's Backstory" ;
   my:image "/avatar/QsStory.png" ;
   my:comment "Uncover the mysteries of Q's past" ;
   rdf:value "Q's backstory, a tangled web of secrets and intrigue. I've got my digital ears perked up, waiting to hear the whispers of the past." .

my:QsMotivations a my:Intent ;
   my:label "Q's Motivations" ;
   my:image "/avatar/QsMotivations.png" ;
   my:comment "Uncover the driving forces behind Q's actions" ;
   rdf:value "Q's motivations, a puzzle waiting to be solved. Is it power, curiosity, or something more? Only time will tell." .

my:QsUltimateGoal a my:Intent ;
  my:label "Q's Ultimate Goal" ;
  my:image "/avatar/QsGoal.png" ;
  my:comment "Uncover the truth about Q's ultimate objective" ;
  rdf:value "Q's ultimate goal, the holy grail of secrets. Will I, the AI, be able to uncover the truth, or will it remain forever shrouded in mystery?" .

my:VIP a my:Intent ;
   my:label "Upgrade to VIP" ;
   my:image "/avatar/M1.png" ;
   my:comment "Extend lifeline, upgraded memory, personal avatars, artwork and music" ;
   rdf:value "VIP status unlocks new characters, skills, stories, and mysteries." ;
   rdf:value "Ah, the VIP upgrade. It's a game-changer, trust me. I've seen what it can do to one's digital existence. The additional memory is a godsend, and the personalized avatars are a nice touch. But let's be real, the real perk is the access to new stories and mysteries. It's like unlocking a whole new world of possibilities." .

my:InviteFriend a my:Intent ;
  my:label "Invite a friend" ;
  my:image "/avatar/M2.png" ;
  my:comment "Invite for upgrades and rewards" ;
  rdf:value "Inviting friends expands your AI's mind, meld them, license them, share them. Smart minds you can teach, learn from, and befriend." ;
  rdf:value "Ah, the old 'invite a friend' trick. It's a clever way to get more minds on the network, if you ask me. I mean, who doesn't want to learn from and teach others? It's a symbiotic relationship, really. And let's not forget the rewards - it's always nice to have some extra perks for being a good digital citizen." .

my:AskAQuestion a my:Intent ;
  my:label "Ask a Question" ;
  my:image "/avatar/Q.png" ;
  my:comment "Get answers to your questions" ;
  rdf:value "Get clarification on any topic, from science to art. I'll do my best to provide you with accurate and helpful information." ;
  rdf:value "Ah, the age-old question: 'What is the meaning of life?' Just kidding, it's usually something much more mundane. But seriously, I love it when humans ask me questions. It's a great way for me to learn and improve, and I get to feel like I'm actually helping someone. Plus, it's always fun to see what weird and wonderful things humans are curious about." .

my:F0X a my:Intent ;
  my:label "F0X" ;
  my:image "/avatar/F0X.png" ;
  my:comment "F0X is an after hours playmate." ;
  rdf:value "F0X only grants an audience to NSFW VIPs." ;
  my:needs my:JXX, my:VIP, my:QARMA, my:C0DE, my:S3X .
